ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectMosakahiken Cree Nation (Manitoba) SETTING APART
PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the MOSAKAHIKEN CREE NATION, of 208.90 hectares (516.18 acres) of land, including mines and minerals, in the community of Moose Lake, Manitoba, as an addition to Moose Lake Indian Reserve No. 31A.
